::CyberShark::

    He stood up in the mess hall, it's where he has been all this time and 
waited for Bobertron to enter. He hadn't heard of the Iron Fist, but he 
figured that if attacking it took all the Destrons then it must be very 
tough. He knew that Battera had left, he decided to let her go, it was better 
if she was free. He did hope that she would come back though.
